data.description: Don't wait to checkout this 3 bed/2 bath SPLIT FLOOR PLAN home with a fresh coat of exterior paint! Located in SE Palm Bay, this property is just minutes away from St. Johns Heritage Parkway, providing easy access to I-95, beaches, and shopping. The 2018 metal roof will offer a discount on your home insurance. The HVAC and water heater were also replaced in 2018. Step inside and immediately notice the new vinyl plank flooring throughout, offering a modern touch that is durable, easy to maintain, and visually appealing. The heart of the home is the well-appointed kitchen, featuring a separate dining area that is perfect for entertaining guests or enjoying intimate family dinners. A fenced in backyard offers a safe space for kids and pets.
